room_title: Escape room "Dr. Zylchov's Lab" by Escapism Portland in Portland
room_description: Enter the lab of Dr. Zylchov, a scientist in 1970s Eastern Europe. You have stumbled upon a room in an abandoned building, and the door has locked behind you. Dr. Zylchov is up to something in here, and the consequences may be disastrous! Work quickly as the doctor seems to be fond of radiation!
